					"“Outer reinforcement, eh. Don't worry, I updated the software on the internals as well. I got this shit, Bro.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"麻沙音"},
					"“加强了外表啊……没关系，里面我都升级了……交给我吧，哥哥……”",
